data.description: Don’t miss this charming contemporary-style home in the quiet Largo neighborhood. Perfect for first-time homeowners. Located on a kid-friendly street, spacious living room and sun-filled yard. Enjoy this property with a good future potential. Just a little TLC and this home will rise fast in value. New drinking water filtration system already installed. 2020 Roof and 2022 HVAC. Close to Clearwater Beach, just a few minutes drive to supermarkets and the cinema, and walking distance to schools, dog park and playground. Two-car garage, but plenty of the front yard parking. Just 8 minutes to the freeway and downtown Clearwater. SELLERS MOTIVATED!!!! SELLER JUST DROPPED THE LISTING PRICE!!!!! BONUS FOR THE SELLING AGENT. SELLER CONCESSION!!!!DON'T MISS THIS OPPORTUNITY!!!
